# Backend Requirements

Add backend functions:

```text
getRandomNightQuestion(playerId, gameId, roundId)
submitNightQuestionAnswer(gameId, roundId, answerText)
skipNightQuestion(gameId, roundId)
getNightThoughtsForDiscussion(gameId, roundId)
```

Backend rules:

* Only current room/game players can receive questions.
* Dead players should not receive active night questions.
* Spectators should not submit answers.
* Each alive player gets one question per night.
* Player cannot submit multiple answers for the same round.
* Player identity must be based on `userId` or `guestId`, not display name.
* Guest players must be supported.
* Authenticated players must be supported.
* Do not expose role data through question APIs.

