# Night Phase Integration

Current night logic must still work.

Night resolution should depend only on required special actions:

```text
Mafia target submitted
Doctor save submitted if Doctor alive
Detective investigation submitted if Detective alive
```

Do not include Villager question answers in this required action check.

Pseudo logic:

```text
after submitNightAction:
    save action

    if allRequiredNightActionsSubmitted:
        resolveNight()
        moveToDayAnnouncementOrDiscussion()
        broadcastPhaseChange()
    else:
        keepWaiting()
```

Question answer logic:

```text
after submitNightQuestionAnswer:
    save answer
    show waiting state
    do not trigger night resolution unless special role actions are complete separately
```

Timer fallback remains:

```text
if nightTimerEnds:
    resolveNightWithAvailableActions()
    moveToDayAnnouncementOrDiscussion()
    broadcastPhaseChange()
```

