# Acceptance Criteria

* Villagers see a random night question during night phase.
* Villagers can submit or skip the question.
* Villager question answers do not block night resolution.
* Mafia, Doctor, and Detective see their normal action first.
* After special role action is submitted, they also see a night question while waiting.
* Night still resolves immediately when all required special actions are submitted.
* Night still resolves when timer ends.
* The UI does not reveal who has a special role.
* Public messages do not say which role has submitted.
* Guest players can use night questions.
* Authenticated players can use night questions.
* Refresh/reconnect works.
* Optional anonymous Night Thoughts appear during discussion if implemented.
* No hidden role data leaks through the question system.
* Mobile UI works properly.
* Build passes.


